result.title: TCO16 Marathon Round 3
result.content: TCO16 Marathon Round 3 TerrainCrossing started today. It will run for 2 weeks, the top 2 participants will advance to the finals, the top 15 will get t-shirts, and the participants of the first two rounds will finally find out who gets two additional spots in the finals (current unofficial leaderboard). I am the writer; enjoy :-)
